eiving%20%24175%20million%20when%20eBay%20bought%20PayPal%20in%202002%2C%20he%20put%20%24100%20million%20into%20his%20new%20space%20exploration%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202006%2C%20SpaceX%20had%20160%20employees%20and%20%24278%20million%20in%20funding%20from%20NASA%20as%20it%20worked%20to%20launch%20the%20Falcon%201%20rocket.%20However%2C%20the%20fledgling%20company%20looked%20set%20to%20collapse%20after%20its%20first%20three%20launches%20failed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20in%20late%202008%2C%20NASA%20effectively%20saved%20SpaceX%20by%20awarding%20it%20a%20%241.6%20billion%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%2015%20years%2C%20and%20the%20company%20has%20about%2012%2C000%20staff%2C%20is%20valued%20at%20about%20%24137%20billion%20per%20a%20CNBC%20report%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20and%20has%20launched%20240%20Falcon%20rockets.%20That%20success%20has%20only%20come%20under%20Musk's%20highly%20demanding%20and%20intense%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224001%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20SpaceX%20Falcon%209%20rocket%20launches%20against%20a%20dusk%20sky%2C%20with%20a%20SpaceX%20branded%20factory%20visible%20in%20the%20foreground.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a42d964cc8540019cb5bdf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222914%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20SpaceX%20Falcon%209%20rocket%20lifts%20off%20from%20the%20Kennedy%20Space%20Center%2C%20Florida%2C%20in%20May%202020.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Burbank%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EGood%20and%20bad%20Elon%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWalter%20Isaacson%2C%20whose%20biography%20about%20Musk%20will%20be%20published%20in%20September%2C%20said%20he%20witnessed%20the%20billionaire%20go%20into%20%26quot%3Bdemon%20mode%26quot%3B%20with%20%26quot%3Bbrutal%26quot%3B%20moments%20of%20rage%20that%20could%20promote%20productivity%20but%20lacked%20empathy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Jim%20Cantrell%2C%20who%20helped%20set%20up%20SpaceX%2C%20tol