istopher-nolan-ranked%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anti-Terror%20Agency%20Charges%203%20Terrorists%20Linked%20To%20Khalistani%20Groups%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%20has%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20against%20three%20%26quot%3Bindividual%20terrorists%26quot%3B%20associated%20with%20banned%20Khalistani%20outfits%20BKI%20and%20KTF%2C%20exposing%20their%20international%20nodes%20involved%20in%20the%20recruitment%20and%20handling%20of%20India-based%20terror%20operatives%2C%20an%20official%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20other%20associates%20working%20for%20the%20Babbar%20Khalsa%20International%20and%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20were%20also%20named%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20filed%20before%20a%20special%20court%20on%20Sunday%2C%20also%20highlighting%20a%20complex%20mechanism%20of%20fund%20raising%20for%20the%20two%20outfits%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20said%20it%20is%20also%20investigating%20the%20links%20of%2016%20other%20absconding%20and%20arrested%20accused%20associated%20with%20the%20BKI%20and%20KTF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20three%20notorious%20gangsters-turned-terrorists%20and%20drug-smugglers%20--%20Harwinder%20Singh%20Sandhu%20alias%20'Rinda'%2C%20Lakhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu%20alias%20'Landa'%20of%20BKI%20and%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20alias%20'Arsh%20Dala'%20of%20KTF%20--%20are%20based%20outside%20the%20country%20and%20have%20created%20their%20own%20networks%20of%20operatives%20there%20to%20carry%20out%20terror%20activities%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThrough%20this%20complex%20network%20of%20operatives%20based%20abroad%2C%20they%20have%20been%20recruiting%2C%20motivating%20and%20handling%20their%20associates%20in%20India%20to%20carry%20out%20terrorist%20activities%2C%20extortion%20and%20cross-border%20smuggling%20of%20weapons%20and%20drugs%20into%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20also%20have%20linkages%20with%20major%20gangs%20operating%20in%20north%20India%2C%20including%20local%20gangsters%2C%20organized%20criminal%20syndicates%20and%20networks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20NIA%2C%20Rinda%20is%20a%20very%20important%20BKI%20member%20and%20Khalistani%20operative.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20year%202018-19%2C%20he%20fled%20to%20Pakistan%20illegally%20and%20is%20currently%20living%20there%20under%20the%20patronage%20of%20ISI%2C%20and%20is%20involved%20in%20the%20commission%20of%20terrorist%20activities%20against%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRinda%20is%20involved%20in%20various%20offences%20like%20smuggling%20of%20arms%2C%20ammunition%20explosives%20and%20drugs%20into%20Indian%20territory%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20recruitment%20of%20BKI%20operatives%2C%20murders%2C%20raising%20funds%20for%20BKI%20through%20extortion%20in%20the%20states%20of%20Punjab%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%20Rinda%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20many%20terrorist%20activities%2C%20including%20the%20RPG%20attack%20on%20the%20Punjab%20Police%20Intelligence%20headquarters%20in%20May%202022%2C%20and%20was%20declared%20an%20%26quot%3Bindividual%20terrorist%26quot%3B%20along%20with%20Dala%20and%20Landa%20by%20the%20centre%2C%20the%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoga%20resident%20Dala%20is%20an%20infamous%20gangster%20who%20left%20for%20Canada%20sometime%20back%20and%20came%20in%20contact%20with%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20who%20was%20the%20chief%20of%20proscribed%20terrorist%20organization%20KTF%2C%20according%20to%20the%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20engaged%20in%20the%20recruitment%20of%20youth%20and%20formation%20of%20terrorist%20gangs%20for%20carrying%20out%20extortion%20for%20raising%20funds%20for%20KTF%20and%20for%20carrying%20out%20targeted%20killing%20of%20businessmen%20and%20leaders%20of%20particular%20communities%20in%20Punjab%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%20Landa%20of%20Tarn%20Taran%20was%20initially%20involved%20in%20criminal%20and%20gangster%20activities%20and%20left%20for%20Canada%20in%202017%20where%20he%20came%20in%20contact%20with%20Rinda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELanda%20started%20working%20for%20the%20BKI%20and%20emerged%20as%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20a%20number%20of%20terrorist%20incidents%2C%20including%20the%20RPG%20attack%20on%20Punjab%20Police%20Intelligence%20headquarters%20and%20RPG%20attack%20on%20Sarhali%20Police%20station%20in%20Tarn%20Taran%20in%20December%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20the%20mastermind%20of%20the%20conspiracy%20to%20kill%20Punjab%20Police%20Sub%20Inspector%20Dilbagh%20Singh%20in%20August%20last%20year%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20other%20foreign-based%20chargesheeted%20operatives%20of%20BKI%20include%20Harjot%20Singh%20who%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20USA%2C%20Kashmir%20Singh%20Galwaddi%2C%20who%20is%20absconding%20in%20the%20Nabha%20Jailbreak%20case%20and%20suspected%20to%20be%20presently%20in%20Nepal%2C%20and%20Landa's%20broyher%20Tarsem%20Singh%2C%20currently%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGurjant%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20hiding%20in%20Australia%2C%20is%20amongst%20the%20foreign-based%20nodes%20of%20KTF%20who%20has%20been%20chargesheeted%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20adding%20other%20accused%20chargesheeted%20are%20Deepak%20Ranga%20and%20Lucky%20Khokhar%20alias%20'Denis'%2C%20who%20were%20recruited%20by%20foreign-based%20handlers%20for%20carrying%20out%20terror%20activities%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690131180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-12%2F9cmll0r_nia-gen