c%20violence%20as%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20it%20took%20time%20to%20be%20contained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProof%20of%20state%20complicity%20can%20clearly%20be%20discerned%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20what%20started%20out%20as%20a%20purely%20ethnic-communal%20violence%20was%20later%20on%20attempted%20to%20be%20portrayed%20by%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20as%20the%20state's%20war%20on%20'narco%20terrorists'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Haokip%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fopinion%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-violence-could-not-be-contained-because-of-complicity-of-biren-singh-government-618797-2023-07-22%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20an%20opinion%20article%20for%20India%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2010%20MLAs%20who%20wrote%20the%20letter%20in%20May%2C%20seven%20of%20them%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20had%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20violence%20was%20perpetrated%20by%20the%20valley-majority%20Meitei%20community%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Btacitly%20supported%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20BJP-run%20state%20government.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-violence-manipur-chief-minister-rejects-separate-administration-demand-for-kuki-areas-4035326%5C%22%3Ehad%20rejected%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bthe%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20Manipur%20will%20be%20protected%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'narco%20terrorists'%20narrative%20seemed%20to%20be%20aimed%20at%20justifying%20the%20use%20of%20state%20forces%20to%20aid%20the%20radicalised%20Meitei%20militia%20in%20attacking%20and%20burning%20down%20Kuki-Zo%20settlements%20in%20the%20foothills%20surrounding%20the%20Imphal%20valley%2C%20beyond%20which%20it%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20hold%20much%20water%2C%20Paolienlal%20Haokip%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20conflict%20over%20rights%20under%20the%20Constitution%20which%20had%20been%20simmering%20since%20the%20pre-statehood%20days%20was%20another