to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20on%20Sunday%2C%20July%2023%20condemning%20the%20sexual%20assault%20of%20three%20Kuki%20women%20on%20May%204%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%5C%22%3Erecently%20came%20to%20light%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20appealed%20to%20the%20president%20to%20call%20for%20an%20independent%20investigation%20into%20all%20acts%20of%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20ensure%20that%20fact-finding%20and%20peace%20missions%20to%20the%20state%20are%20free%20from%20intimidation%2C%20and%20guarantee%20that%20there%20are%20no%20arbitrary%20additions%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20list%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%203%2C256%20signatories%20to%20its%20appeal%20include%20environmental%20activist%20Medha%20Patkar%2C%20activist%20and%20former%20bureaucrat%20Harsh%20Mander%2C%20and%20poet%20Meena%20Kandasamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENAPM%20is%20an%20umbrella%20organisation%20of%20civil%20society%20organisations%2C%20grassroots%20movements%20and%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20letter%20to%20the%20president%20began%20by%20criticising%20the%20state%20police%E2%80%99s%20delay%20in%20arresting%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20the%20May%204%20incident%20%E2%80%93%20in%20which%20two%20Kuki%20women%20were%20filmed%20being%20paraded%20naked%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20%E2%80%93%20despite%20many%20perpetrators%20being%20visible%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20proceeds%20to%20urge%20the%20president%20to%20visit%20the%20state%20given%20her%20stature%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20she%20is%20a%20woman%20belonging%20to%20a%20tribal%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20signatories%20also%20say%20that%20it%20is%20incumbent%20upon%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20to%20resign%20from%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20extremely%20unfortunate%20and%20unforgivable%20that%20the%20most%20brazen%20and%20divisive%20politics%20is%20being%20played%20by%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day%2C%20along%20with%20majoritarian%2C%20rightist%20forces%2C%20over%20the%20lives%20of%20vulnerable%20sections%20within%20Manipur%2C%20while%20allowing%20hate%20crimes%20to%20go%20on%20unhindered%20and%20unpunished.%20In%20fact%2C%20given%20their%20colossal%20failure%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Manipur%20must%20be%20asked%20to%20immediately%20step%20down%2C%20owning%20moral%20and%20legal%20responsibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%E2%80%99s%20second%20appeal%20to%20the%20president%20%E2%80%93%20that%20civil%20society%20missions%20visiting%20the%20state%20must%20be%20free%20from%20intimidation%20by%20the%20government%20%E2%80%93%20comes%20in%20light%20of%20FIRs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-violence-fir-fact-finding-team%5C%22%3Efiled%20against%20members%20of%20a%20National%20Federation%20of%20Indian%20Women%20commission%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20visited%20the%20state%20and%20found%20that%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%20violence%E2%80%9D%20contributed%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20turmoil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20points%20raised%20by%20NAPM%E2%80%99s%20letter%20include%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DO4v9u8GZ1Yg%5C%22%3Eblanket%20internet%20ban%20in%20the%20state%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fopinion%2Ftroubling-questions-on-a-wrenching-video-101690034681323.html%5C%22%3Edelay%20by%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20following%20up%20with%20authorities%20after%20receiving%20information%20on%20the%20May%204%20incident%2C%20and%20a%20note%20of%20caution%20against%20the%20upcoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Finterview-why-there-is-mistrust-about-proposed-changes-to-forest-conservation-law%5C%22%3EForest%20Conservation%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20text%20of%20the%20English%20version%20of%20the%20letter%20has%20been%20reproduced%20below.%20Please%20see%20the%20embedded%20PDF%20for%20the%20full%20list%20of%20signatories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3EAll-India%20Appeal%C2%A0%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3Efrom%203%2C200%20%2B%20concerned%20citizens%C2%A0%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3Eto%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20President%20on%20Manipur%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3EIntervene%20Immediately%20to%20Ensure%20Peace%20and%20Justice%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnMadam%20Draupadi%20Murmu%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnHon%E2%80%99ble%20President%20of%20India%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnRashtrapati%20Bhavan%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnNew%20Delhi%2C%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESub%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Seeking%20your%20urgent%20intervention%20and%20visit%20for%20restoration%20of%20peace%20and%20justice%20in%20strife-torn%20Manipur%20and%20support%20to%20violated%20Kuki-Zo%20women.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadam%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20the%20undersigned%20organisations%20and%20activists%20associated%20with%20the%20National%20Alliance%20of%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movements%2C%20numerous%20other%20progressive%20organisations%20and%20citizens%20from%20across%20India%2C%20write%20to%20you%20with%20a%20fervent%20and%20urgent%20appeal%2C%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20humanitarian%20crisis%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20almost%20three%20months%2C%20the%20North-Eastern%20state%20of%20Manipur%20has%20been%20in%20a%20state%20of%20unprecedented%20turmoil%20and%20violence%2C%20owing%20to%20ethnic%20clashes%20and%20miserable%20failure%20of%20the%20Central%20and%20State%20Governments%2C%20in%20restoring%20normalcy.%20What%20began%20as%20popular%20resistance%20to%20the%20questionable%20proposal%20to%20include%20non-STs%20(Meiteis)%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20list%2C%20soon%20snowballed%20into%20a%20state-wide%20crisis%20of%20unimaginable%20proportions%2C%20with%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20conflict.%C2%A0%20The%20trail%20of%20violence%20has%20left%20at%20least%20150%20people%20dead%2C%20entire%20villages%20razed%20down%20and%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20displaced%2C%20amidst%20untold%20suffering%20for%20both%20the%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20seems%20to%20have%20finally%20%E2%80%98shook%20the%20nation%E2%80%99%20and%20compelled%20the%20powers-that-be%2C%20especially%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(who%20has%20been%20silent%20so%20far)%2C%20to%20%E2%80%98speak%20up%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20the%20recent%20viral%20video%20of%20three%20Kuki-Zo%20tribal%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20in%20full%20public%20glare%2C%20way%20back%20on%20May%204%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district.%20In%20the%20same%20instance%2C%20the%20two%20male%20members%20of%20the%20family%20were%20killed%20by%20the%20mob.%20While%20an%20FIR%20was%20filed%202%20months%20back%2C%20the%20first%20and%20(only)%20arrest%20happened%20on%20July%2020%2C%20after%20national%20outrage%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20large%20mob%20of%20identifiable%20men%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Mr.%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20own%20chilling%20statement%2C%20this%20is%20just%20one%20instance%20which%20has%20come%20to%20light%2C%20out%20of%20more%20than%20hundred%20other%20such%20cases!%20Clearly%2C%20this%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98tip%20of%20the%20scary%20iceberg%E2%80%99%20and%C2%A0a%20comprehensive%20inquiry%20is%20needed%20to%20ensure%20due%20legal%20process%20and%20accountability%20of%20violators%20and%20authorities%20in%20all%20such%20instances.%20Instead%20of%20clamping%20down%20on%20internet%20services%2C%20the%20Govt.%20must%20clamp%20down%20on%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-video-arrest-biren-singh-supreme-court%5C%22%3EManipur%20Video%3A%20CM%20Biren%20Says%20%E2%80%98100s%20of%20Similar%20Cases%E2%80%99%20Happened%3B%20SC%20Takes%20Cognisance%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadam%2C%20it%20is%20absolutely%20unacceptable%20and%20unjustifiable%20that%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20are%20used%20as%20sites%20of%20brutal%20violence%20by%20the%20State%20and%20supremacist%2C%20patriarchal%20forces.%20While%20the%20majoritarian%20mobs%20and%20police%20are%20directly%20culpable%2C%20the%20inaction%20and%20complicity%20of%20those%20higher-up%20in%20the%20echelons%20of%20power%20needs%20questioning%20too.%20Even%20institutions%20like%20the%20NCW%2C%20which%20have%20been%20in%20receipt%20of%20complaints%20of%20sexual%20violence%20and%20rape%20since%20more%20than%20a%20month%20refused%20to%20act%20for%20so%20long!%C2%A0The%20intervention%20of%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20also%20sadly%20been%20a%20case%20of%20too%20little%2C%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20extremely%20unfortunate%20and%20unforgivable%20that%20the%20most%20brazen%20and%20divisive%20politics%20is%20being%20played%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20the%20day%2C%20along%20with%20majoritarian%2C%20rightist%20forces%2C%20over%20the%20lives%20of%20vulnerable%20sections%20within%20Manipur%2C%20while%20allowing%20hate%20crimes%20to%20go%20on%20unhindered%20and%20unpunished.%C2%A0Infact%2C%20given%20their%20colossal%20failure%2C%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20and%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Manipur%20must%20be%20asked%20to%20immediately%20step%20down%2C%20owning%20moral%20and%20legal%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadam%2C%20we%20appeal%20to%20you%3B%20as%20a%20woman%2C%20as%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20Adivasi%20community%2C%20custodian%20of%20tribal%20rights%20and%20a%20holder%20of%20the%20highest%20office%20under%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20to%20immediately%20intervene%20in%20the%20light%20of%20these%20grave%20and%20deeply%20disturbing%20circumstances%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20urge%20you%20to%20immediately%20visit%20Manipur%20and%20interact%20with%20the%20affected%20people%2C%20especially%20the%20women%20who%20have%20suffered%20grave%20injustice%20and%20give%20them%20necessary%20assurance.%20The%20women%20of%20Manipur%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20tribal%20communities%2C%20need%20a%20calming%2C%20balming%20support%20which%20only%20someone%20of%20your%20stature%20can%20provide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20appeal%20to%20your%20good%20conscience%20to%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Call%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20and%20time-bound%20judicial%20inquiry%20into%20all%20acts%20of%20violence%2C%20so%20that%20all%20the%20accused%20who%20have%20perpetrated%20heinous%20crimes%20are%20arrested%2C%20including%20under%20SC%20%26amp%3B%20ST%20(PoA)%20Act%2C%20speedy%20trial%20and%20conviction%2C%20with%20life%20is%20ensured.%20Likewise%2C%20such%20an%20inquiry%20must%20fix%20the%20accountability%20of%20all%20law%20enforcement%20and%20political%20authorities%2C%20at%20all%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Ensure%20independent%20fact-finding%2C%20peace%20and%20justice%20missions%20of%20civil%20society%20are%20allowed%20to%20visit%20Manipur%2C%20especially%20the%20women%2C%20and%20the%20Govt%20refrains%20from%20intimidatory%20tactics%20of%20stopping%20or%20filing%20FIRs%20against%20those%20visiting%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Uphold%20tribal%20rights%20and%20guarantee%20to%20the%20people%20that%20there%20shall%20be%20no%20unjust%20and%20arbitrary%20change%20in%20the%20list%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-talked-about-the-manipur-violence-but-did-he-really%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20Talked%20About%20the%20Manipur%20Violence.%20But%20Did%20He%20Really%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20hope%20you%20will%20do%20all%20that%20is%20possible%2C%20as%20head%20of%20the%20State%20to%20appeal%20for%20inter-community%20harmony%20and%20ensure%20peace%2C%20with%20normalcy%20is%20restored%20back%2C%20both%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20valley%20of%20Manipur%2C%20and%20adequate%20safety%20is%20ensured%20to%20those%20in%20vulnerable%20situations%2C%20especially%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20and%20all%20the%20violators%2C%20at%20all%20levels%2C%20are%20brought%20to%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20all%20this%20mayhem%2C%20the%20Union%20Govt.%20is%20also%20trying%20to%20make%20far-reaching%20amendments%20to%20forest%20laws%20of%20the%20country%2C%20which%20will%20result%20in%20massive%20diversion%20of%20forest%20land%20across%20India%2C%20including%20in%20the%20North-East%2C%20loot%20of%20forest%20resources%20by%20private-corporate%20entities%20and%20displacement%20of%20adivasis%20and%20forest-dwelling%20communities.%20We%20urge%20you%20to%20not%20assent%20to%20these%20amendments%2C%20if%20and%20when%20they%20come%20to%20you%20from%20the%20Parliament%2C%20and%20insist%20on%20compliance%20with%20provisions%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%2C%202006%20and%20other%20enabling%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYours%20sincerely%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Roop%20Rekha%20Verma%2C%20Medha%20Patkar%2C%20Harsh%20Mander%2C%20Prof.%20Virginius%20Xaxa%2C%20Ruth%20Manorama%2C%20Meena%20Kandasamy%2C%20Dr.%20Gabriele%20Dietrich%2C%20Prafulla%20Samantara%2C%20Elina%20Horo%2C%20SR%20Darapuri%2C%20Prof.%20Sandeep%20Pandey%2C%20Agnes%20Kharshiing%2C%20Holiram%20Terang%2C%20Prof.%20Rama%20Melkote%2C%20Jitendra%20Paswan%2C%20Ramarao%20Dora%2C%20Anant%20Phadke%2C%20Kalyani%20Menon%20Sen%2C%20Kavitha%20Kuruganti%2C%20Ulka%20Mahajan%2C%20Deepa%20Pawar%2C%20Diana%2C%20Tavers%2C%20Dr.%20Maroona%20Murmu%2C%20Nalini%20Nayak%2C%20Tshering%20Chopel%20Lepcha%2C%20Gautam%20Mody%2C%20Henri%20Tiphagne%2C%20Sugathakumari%2C%20Romita%20Reang%2C%20Madhu%20Bhushan%2C%20Steffi%20Lawbei%2C%20Manshi%20Asher%2C%20Aquila%20Khan%2C%20Priyanka%20Samy%2C%20Lalita%20Ramdas%2C%20Nandita%20Narain%2C%20Shaktiman%20Ghosh%2C%20Abhirami%2C%20Raina%2C%20Syed%20Ali%20Nadeem%20and%203200%2B%20others%20from%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20Appeal%20along%20with%20list%20of%20all%20signatories%20is%20attached%20as%20a%20PDF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F660684796%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-QssaVqW5Xftz1hA5BwJ9%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%220.7729220222793488%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22All-India%20Appeal%20to%20the%20Hon'Ble%20President%20on%20Manipur%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690128575000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F22162232%2FFvXbR35WcAASmrA.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnapm-letter-with-3000-plus-signatories-urges-prez-to-visit-manipur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20letter%20to%20President%20Draupadi%20Murmu%20by%20the%20National%20Alliance%20of%20People's%20Movements%20had%20over%203%2C000%20signatories.%20It%20also%20called%20for%20the%20resignation%20of%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Manipur%20CM%20Biren%20Singh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnapm-letter-with-3000-plus-signatories-urges-prez-to-visit-manipur%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Want%20Your%20Daughter%20Dead%20Or%20Alive%3F%5C%22%3A%20Mother%20Of%20Murdered%20Manipur%20Woman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20phone%20call%20to%20find%20her%20daughter's%20whereabouts%20was%20a%20spine-chilling%20experience%20for%20a%20tribal%20woman%20in%20Manipur.%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20want%20your%20daughter%20dead%20or%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20voice%20at%20the%20other%20end.%20It%20was%20a%20woman.%20The%20mother%20was%20not%20really%20being%20given%20a%20choice.%20Later%2C%20they%20were%20informed%20that%20her%20daughter%20was%20dead.%20Her%20blood%20and%20hair%20were%20found%20plastered%20on%20the%20walls%20of%C2%A0%20a%20building%20in%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20is%20yet%20to%20receive%20the%20body.%20%26quot%3BI%20still%20cannot%20accept%20the%20fact%20and%20I%20still%20sometimes%20hope%20that%20my%20daughter%20will%20return%20because%20I%20haven't%20seen%20her%20with%20my%20own%20eyes.%20Even%20right%20now%20her%20dad%20is%20still%20at%20the%20hospital%20in%20Senapati.%20I%20still%20cannot%20believe%20what%20happened%20to%20my%20daughter.%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20daughter%20was%20one%20of%20the%20two%20young%20women%20who%20were%20gangraped%20and%20murdered%20at%20a%20car%20wash%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20May%205%2C%20two%20days%20after%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20gagged%20and%20locked%20in%20the%20room%20by%20seven%20men%2C%20said%20eye-witnesses.%20They%20had%20screamed%20and%20pleaded%2C%20but%20their%20attackers%20did%20not%20relent.%20Sources%20said%20a%20co-worker%2C%20who%20reportedly%20witnessed%20the%20incident%2C%20said%20the%20women%20in%20the%20mob%20encouraged%20the%20men%20to%20sexually%20assault%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20have%20allegedly%20been%20kept%20in%20the%20morgue%20at%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(JNIMS)%20hospital%20in%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20the%20violence%20I%20was%20worried%2C%20so%20I%20had%20called%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman's%20mother%20told%20NDTV.%20%26quot%3BA%20woman%20picked%20up%20the%20phone.%20She%20questioned%20if%20I%20want%20my%20daughter%20dead%20or%20alive%20and%20hung%20up.%20My%20mind%20went%20blank%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20heart%20patient%20and%20because%20of%20that%2C%20my%20family%20doesn't%20tell%20me%20anything.%20So%2C%20I%20called%20my%20children%20together%20and%20spoke%20to%20them%20about%20what%20was%20happening.%20After%20that%20I%20did%20not%20receive%20any%20calls.%20After%20some%20days%20I%20received%20a%20call%20and%20was%20told%20what%20had%20happened%20to%20my%20daughter%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20atrocities%20took%20place%20the%20same%20day%20two%20women%20were%20paraded%20naked%20around%2040%20km%20away.%20The%20video%2C%20which%20surfaced%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20had%20evoked%20shock%20and%20outrage%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrimes%20against%20women%20in%20Manipur%20in%20this%20latest%20wave%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20started%20making%20headlines%20only%20after%20the%20horror%20video%20of%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%20surfaced.%20At%20least%20125%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20and%20more%20than%2040%2C000%20displaced%20since%20the%20violence%20erupted%20on%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20have%20confirmed%20that%20no%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%20in%20this%20case%20so%20far.%20The%20Manipur%20police%20are%20currently%20examining%20thousands%20of%20complaints%20related%20to%20various%20crimes%2C%20including%20weapon%20looting%2C%20arson%2C%20killings%2C%20and%20assaults%20on%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690128420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F7q2a0i9o_manipur-violence-ani_625x300_30_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-want-your-daughter-dead-or-alive-mother-of-murdered-manipur-woman-4234616%22%2C