0for%20Women%20Development%20and%20Child%20Nutrition%20Pratibha%20Shukla%20on%20Sunday%20advised%20people%20that%20if%20tomatoes%20are%20expensive%2C%20grow%20them%20at%20home%20or%20stop%20eating%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shukla%20participated%20in%20the%20plantation%20drive%20under%20the%20UP%20Government's%20massive%20tree%20plantation%20program%20and%20planted%20saplings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20tomatoes%20are%20expensive%2C%20people%20should%20grow%20them%20at%20home.%20If%20you%20stop%20eating%20tomatoes%2C%20the%20prices%20will%20inevitably%20come%20down.%20You%20can%20also%20eat%20lemon%20instead%20of%20tomato.%20If%20nobody%20is%20eating%20tomatoes%2C%20the%20prices%20will%20come%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Shukla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20an%20example%20of%20the%20nutrition%20garden%20in%20Asahi%20village%2C%20the%20UP%20Minister%20said%20that%20there%20is%20a%20solution%20to%20this%20inflation%2C%20plant%20tomatoes%20at%20home.%20They%20are%20expensive%20all%20the%20time%20and%20if%20you%20do%20not%20eat%20tomatoes%20then%20use%20lemon%2C%20whatever%20is%20more%20expensive%2C%20discard%20it.%20It%20will%20automatically%20become%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20made%20a%20nutrition%20garden%20in%20Asahi%20village%2C%20the%20women%20in%20the%20village%20have%20made%20a%20nutrition%20garden%2C%20and%20tomatoes%20can%20also%20be%20planted%20in%20it.%20There%20is%20a%20solution%20to%20this%20inflation%2C%20this%20is%20not%20new%2C%20tomatoes%20are%20expensive%20all%20the%20time.%20If%20you%20do%20not%20eat%20tomatoes%20then%20use%20lemon%2C%20whatever%20is%20more%20expensive%2C%20discard%20it%2C%20it%20will%20automatically%20become%20cheaper%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Minister%20of%20State%20Consumer%20Affairs%2C%20Food%20and%20Public%20Distribution%2C%20Ashwini%20Kumar%20Choubey%20on%20Friday%20said%20that%20the%20Department%20of%20Consumer%20Affairs%20monitors%20the%20daily%20