untry%20is%20struggling%20with%20inflation%20and%20unemployment.%20The%20country%20is%20trying%20to%20avoid%20the%20onslaught%20of%20an%20incompetent%20and%20merciless%20government.%20That's%20why%20we%20all%20have%20come%20together%20to%20save%20the%20country.%20The%20same%20happened%20in%201977%2C%20even%20today%20the%20same%20dictatorial%20government%20is%20ruling%20the%20country%20and%20it%20has%20to%20be%20removed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Punjab%20Congress%20President%20Amarinder%20Singh%20Raja%20Warring%20has%20called%20the%20inclusion%20of%20AAP%20in%20alliance%20'INDIA'%2C%20'unacceptable'.%20He%20alleged%20that%20AAP%20has%20targeted%20his%20party%20leaders%20and%20one%20of%20his%20leaders%2C%20OP%20Soni%20was%20forcibly%20put%20in%20Jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20Punjab%20LoP%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Partap%20Singh%20Bajwa%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPunjab%20Congress%20unit%20is%20completely%20against%20this%20(forming%20an%20alliance%20with%20AAP)...%20I%20will%20meet%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20on%20Monday%20and%20will%20request%20him%20to%20not%20forge%20an%20alliance%20with%20them%20(AAP).%20We%20were%20not%20in%20alliance%20with%20them%20in%20past%20and%20will%20not%20be%20in%20future%20also.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20alliance%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20has%20been%20named%20INDIA%20(Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20president%20of%20the%20main%20opposition%20Congress%20party%2C%20said%20INDIA%20stood%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BIndian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%26quot%3B.%20The%20development%20came%20as%20top%20leaders%20of%2026%20Opposition%20parties%20from%20across%20the%20country%20met%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20discuss%20a%20united%20strategy%20to%20take%20on%20the%20ruling%20NDA%20alliance%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20the%202024