.%20Surely%2C%20Democracy%20cannot%20be%20about%20disruption%20and%20disturbance%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20pained%20and%20anguished%20to%20indicate%20to%20you%20that%20disruption%20and%20disturbance%20have%20been%20weaponised%20as%20strategic%20means%20to%20taint%20the%20temples%20of%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vice%20president%20said%20empowerment%20of%20human%20resources%20is%20a%20vital%20ingredient%20in%20nation%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYouth%20must%20empower%20themselves%20--%20not%20by%20political%20intoxication%20but%20through%20capacity%20building%20and%20personality%20development%20with%20the%20ultimate%20objective%20of%20nurturing%20a%20healthy%20environment%20and%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%2C%20he%20said%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Brequirement%20for%20adopting%20this%20policy%26quot%3B%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20sure%20they%20will%20fall%20in%20line%20and%20reap%20the%20harvest%20of%20this%20great%20policy.%20It%20is%20based%20on%20skill-based%20courses%2C%20vocational%20training%20and%20giving%20a%20new%20dimension%20to%20our%20educational%20learning.%20It%20is%20crucial%20for%20students%20to%20become%20innovators%20and%20entrepreneurs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20address%2C%20he%20highlighted%20the%20%26quot%3Bimpactful%26quot%3B%20visit%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20the%20US%20and%20France%2C%20while%20noting%20that%20the%20entire%20world%20is%20eager%20to%20partner%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia's%20relevance%20in%20resolution%20of%20global%20issues%20was%20never%20so%20prominent%20as%20it%20is%20today.%20But%20friends%2C%20when%20India%20grows%2C%20when%20you%20avail%20opportunity%20there%20are%20challenges%20too.%20Your%20progress%20cannot%20be%20to%20the%20liking%20of%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20forces%20with%20sinister%20designs%20who%20want%20to%20taint%20and%20tarnish%20your%20institutions%20of%20growth.%20Unfortunately%2C%20some%20are%20among%20us.%20I%20appeal%20to%20young%20minds%20to%20take%20the%20initiative%20and%20neutralise%20these%20forces%20through%20their%20actions.%20No%20doubt%20you%20will%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20called%20upon%20the%20youngsters%20to%20fully%20subscribe%20to%20economic%20nationalism%20with%20all%20their%20energy%20and%20enthusiasm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20in%20the%20national%20interest%20to%20compromise%20economic%20nationalism%20for%20fiscal%20gain%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20the%20present%20norm%20and%20government%20mechanism%20is%20of%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20where%20corruption%20has%20no%20place%2C%20he%20opined%20that%20%26quot%3Bstakeholders%20in%20corruption%20will%20marshal%20all%20forces%20to%20find%20cover%20and%20effect%20escape%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20violators%20of%20law%20--%20no%20one%20can%20claim%20whatever%20lineage%20you%20might%20come%20from%20--%20are%20accountable%20to%20the%20law.%20The%20avenues%20for%20violators%20of%20the%20law%20have%20been%20plugged.%20It%20is%20concerning%20that%20when%20the%20judicial%20process%20is%20set%20in%20motion%2C%20when%20law%20is%20taking%20its%20own%20course%20why%20should%20those%20feeling%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20law%20take%20to%20the%20streets.%20It%20is%20for%20you%20all%20to%20think%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhankhar%20said%20there%20is%20a%20robust%20mechanism%20of%20grievance%20redressal%20in%20the%20judicial%20system.%20If%20someone%20receives%20a%20notice%20from%20an%20agency%2C%20the%20only%20way%20to%20take%20recourse%20in%20a%20democracy%20is%20through%20lawful%20and%20certainly%20not%20to%20take%20to%