0Florida%20Python%20Challenge%20and%20it%20inspired%20her%20to%20change%20her%20life.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20moved%20from%20Indiana%20to%20Florida%20and%20now%20owns%20a%20guiding%20service%20that%20takes%20people%20on%20python%20hunts.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20she's%20living%20her%20best%20life%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20she%20gets%20bitten%20by%20pythons%20from%20time%20to%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20python%20hunter%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pythonhuntress.com%2Fabout-amy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmy%20Siewe%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20college%2C%20I%20had%20various%20jobs%20in%20the%20pet%20and%20reptile%20industry%2C%20including%20breeding%20snakes%20and%20working%20at%20an%20exotic%20pet%20store%20part-time.%20After%20college%2C%20when%20I%20started%20my%20career%20as%20a%20real%20estate%20broker%20in%20Indiana%2C%20my%20work%20with%20snakes%20became%20more%20of%20a%20hobby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20first%20python%20hunt%20in%20Florida%20in%202019%2C%20I%20knew%20I'd%20found%20my%20calling.%20I%20quit%20my%20job%20and%20moved%20to%20Naples%2C%20Florida%2C%20to%20become%20a%20contracted%20python%20hunter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhy%20I%20hunt%20pythons%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20fascination%20with%20snakes%20started%20when%20I%20was%20very%20young.%20My%20dad%20started%20taking%20me%20out%20to%20the%20creek%2C%20where%20he%20showed%20me%20how%20to%20catch%20all%20kinds%20of%20critters%2C%20including%20snakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20I%20wonder%20why%20I%20couldn't%20have%20developed%20a%20passion%20for%20kittens%2C%20puppies%2C%20or%20something%20a%20little%20more%20%26quot%3Bnormal%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20I%20guess%20I%20was%20just%20born%20to%20love%20snakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20hunting%20pythons%2C%20I'm%20using%20my%20passion%20for%20snakes%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20the%20world.%20People%20don't%20always%20understand%20why%20I%20hunt%20pythons%20when%20I%20love%20snakes.%20But%20because%20of%20my%20fascination%20with%20them%2C%20I'm%20not%20afraid%20of%20the%20pythons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurmese%20pythons%20are%20native%20to%20Southeast%20Asia%20and%20are%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usgs.gov%2Ffaqs%2Fhow-have-invasive-pythons-impacted-florida-ecosystems%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvasive%20species%20in%3C%2Fa%3E%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201992%2C%20Hurricane%20Andrew%20demolished%20a%20python%20breeding%20facility%2C%20sending%20about%20900%20pythons%20into%20the%20same%20general%20area%20of%20the%20Everglades.%20People%20who%20bought%20Burmese%20pythons%20as%20pets%20and%20let%20them%20go%20when%20they%20became%20too%20big%20to%20feed%2C%20house%2C%20and%20handle%20have%20also%20contributed%20to%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20massive%20reptiles%20have%20become%20the%20apex%20predator%20in%20Florida%2C%20and%20they%20have%20a%20voracious%20appetite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20you'll%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiep.berkeley.edu%2Fcontent%2Fburmese-pythons-everglades%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20longer%20see%20some%20animals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20rabbits%2C%20foxes%2C%20raccoons%2C%20and%20opossums%2C%20in%20certain%20parts%20of%20the%20Everglades.%20Burmese%20pythons%20aren't%20picky%20eaters%2C%20either%2C%20so%20they'll%20also%20eat%20birds%20and%20other%20animals%2C%20especially%20as%20their%20main%20food%20sources%20dwindle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20their%20fault%20they're%20here%2C%20and%20I%20absolutely%20hate%20having%20to%20kill%20them.%20To%20preserve%20the%20Everglades%2C%20though%2C%20they%20have%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFrom%20real%20estate%20to%20python%20hunting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EReal%20estate%20is%20an%20established%20industry%20with%20processes%20and%20systems%20in%20place%20to%20follow%2C%20where%20you%20can%20become%20successful%20over%20time%20with%20the%20proper%20dedication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20python%20hunter%20and%20guide%2C%20I%20bring%20my%20love%20of%20snakes%20and%20appetite%20for%20adventure%20to%20the%20hunt%2C%20and%20my%20entrepreneurial%20drive%20to%20the%20business.%20Every%20single%20day%20brings%20something%20new%2C%20and%20I%20thrive%20on%20the%20challenge%20%E2%80%94%20I%20know%20I'm%20living%20my%20best%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20spend%20my%20time%20in%20the%20swamp%2C%20catching%20these%20elusive%20snakes%20on%20the%20move.%20They're%20not%20easy%20to%20find%2C%20since%20they%20don't%20like%20to%20be%20exposed%20and%20spend%20most%20of%20their%20time%20not%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20do%20move%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20travel%20under%20vegetation%2C%20and%20their%20colors%20perfectly%20camouflage%20them%20with%20their%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20leaves%20and%20bushes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b8025e8a4e660019e2fccf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22389%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20a%2017-foot%20python%20hiding%20here.%3Cp%3EAmy%20Siewe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%2C%20we%20have%20to%20hunt%20at%20night%20since%20it's%20so%20hot.%20We%20go%20out%20on%20a%20truck%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bsnake%20deck%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20built-on%20platform%20fitted%20with%20lights%20to%20see%20over%20the%20sides%20%E2%80%94%20driving%20down%20the%20roads%20very%20slowly%2C%20looking%20into%20canals%20and%20the%20grass%2C%20searching%20for%20pythons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20they're%20in%20the%20treeline%2C%20sometimes%20parallel%20to%20the%20road%20or%20even%20crossing%20the%20road.%20They're%20so%20big%2C%20they%20usually%20move%20pretty%20slow%2C%20and%20they%20often%20don't%20see%20us%20as%20predators%20or%20prey%2C%20but%20as%20more%20of%20an%20annoyance.%20When%20they%20get%20spooked%20and%20want%20to%20go%2C%20though%2C%20they%20move%20very%20quickly%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20capture%20even%20more%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22384%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amy%20Siewe%20and%20colleague%20standing%20in%20the%20back%20of%20a%20truck%20at%20night.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b8025e8a4e660019e2fcd1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOut%20on%20the%20truck%2C%20hunting.%3Cp%3EAmy%20Siewe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EPython%20hunting%20isn't%20without%20its%20risks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20started%20out%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwusfnews.wusf.usf.edu%2Fenvironment%2F2022-06-22%2Fwant-to-hunt-pythons-in-florida-this-summer-this-professional-has-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estate-contracted%20python%20hunter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20now%20own%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pythonhuntress.com%2Fguided-hunts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eguiding%20service%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20take%20people%20on%20python%20hunts.%20I%20love%20this%20because%20I%20get%20to%20head%20out%20into%20the%20Everglades%20with%20people%20who've%20never%20gone%20out%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20explain%20all%20of%20the%20laws%20in%20place%20for%20hunting%20the%20pythons%20humanely%2C%20teach%20them%20how%20to%20spot%20and%20catch%20the%20pythons%2C%20and%20show%20them%20the%20proper%20way%20to%20euthanize%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20capture%20pythons%20alive%20and%20use%20a%20captive%20bolt%20gun%20to%20euthanize%20them.%20The%20American%20Veterinary%20Association%20has%20approved%20this%20method%20for%20humane%20euthanasia%20of%20Burmese%20pythons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20pythons%20aren't%20venomous%2C%20they're%20incredibly%20strong%20and%20powerful%20animals.%20Dodging%20their%20coils%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20tricky%2C%20and%20it's%20definitely%20more%20dangerous%20to%20catch%20the%20ones%20over%2015%20feet%20long!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22384%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amy%20Siewe%20holding%20a%2017'3%26quot%3B%20python.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b8025e8a4e660019e2fcd3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20personal%20record%3A%20A%2017%E2%80%993%E2%80%9D%20python%20I%20caught%20by%20myself%20that%20weighed%20110%20pounds%3Cp%3EAmy%20Siewe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20have%20a%20mouth%20full%20of%20razor-sharp%20teeth.%20I've%20been%20bitten%20many%20times%2C%20and%20I%20can%20say%20those%20bites%20aren't%20fun.%20They%20bleed%20quite%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20there's%20always%20the%20chance%20of%20running%20into%20an%20alligator%2C%20panther%2C%20bear%2C%20or%20venomous%20snake.%20However%2C%20these%20animals%20tend%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bloody%20hand%20from%20a%20python%20bite.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b8025e76558a00189db546%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22366%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20python%20bite.%3Cp%3EAmy%20Siewe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20I%20respect%20the%20pythons%20I%20hunt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20want%20to%20use%20as%20much%20of%20the%20python%20as%20possible%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20make%20good%20eating%2C%20since%20their%20meat%20is%20very%20chewy%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.palmbeachpost.com%2Fstory%2Fweather%2F2020%2F11%2F19%2Fflorida-python-its-whats-dinner%2F6328020002%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efull%20of%20mercury%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20their%20skin%20is%20gorgeous%20and%20makes%20beautiful%20lea