%2C%20but%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2F16-electrocuted-at-river-project-site-in-uttarakhands-chamoli-district%2Farticleshow%2F101967546.cms%5C%22%3Edid%20not%20prevent%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20two%20subsequent%20leakages%20that%20took%20place%20soon%20after.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20246px)%2085vw%2C%20246px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22246%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20joint%20venture%20plant%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20much%20publicised%20Namami%20Gange%20project%20%E2%80%93%20for%20cleaning%20the%20polluted%20Ganges%20%E2%80%93%20and%20was%20located%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20a%20major%20tributary%20of%20the%20Ganges%2C%20the%20Alaknanda.%20The%20sewage%20treatment%20job%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fdehradun-case-registered-against-supervisor-of-namami-gange-stp-in-chamoli-electrocution-incident-101689878437723.html%5C%22%3Ehad%20been%20outsourced%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20private%20companies%20named%20Jai%20Bhushan%20Malik%20Contractors%20and%20Confident%20Engineering%20India.%20A%20safety%20audit%20of%20the%20plant%20has%20now%20been%20ordered.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kiplingsociety.co.uk%2Fpoem%2Fpoems_englishflag.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKipling%20had%20once%20asked%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20an%20interesting%20question%3A%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20what%20should%20they%20know%20of%20England%20who%20only%20England%20know%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20after%20watching%20repeated%20tragedies%20striking%20power%20plants%20in%20this%20eco-fragile%20zone%2C%20as%20well%20as%20large%20chunks%20of%20forests%2C%20entire%20hillsides%2C%20vital%20bridges%20and%20national%20highways%20being%20swept%20away%20in%20the%20monsoons%20by%20raging%20rivers%2C%20if%20we%20ask%20how%20much%20our%20engineers%20and%20terrain%20experts%20know%20the%20Himalayas%20that%20they%20are%20hell-bent%20on%20%E2%80%98developing%E2%80%99%20as%20tourist%20areas%2C%20the%20likely%20answer%20would%20be%3A%20%E2%80%9CMaybe%20not%20nearly%20enough.%20Maybe%20not%20at%20all.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUp%20until%20the%201850s%2C%20the%20Uttarakhand%20hills%20were%20pristine%20hunting%20grounds%20for%20British%20officials%20craving%20cool%20vacations%20after%20spending%20time%20in%20the%20hot%20and%20dusty%20plains%20handing%20unequal%20laws%20to%20those%20they%20considered%20were%20the%20savage%20races.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%201857%2C%20when%20the%20Crown%20took%20over%2C%20civil%20engineering%20works%20by%20British%20engineers%20first%20began%20on%20a%20planned%20scale.%20Nainital%20had%20already%20been%20built%20and%20rebuilt%20after%20a%20quake.%20In%201887%2C%20they%20built%20the%20town%20of%20Lansdowne%20to%20house%20the%20Garhwal%20Rifles%2C%20who%20guarded%20the%20difficult%20terrain%20along%20the%20Indo-Tibet%20border.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20motor%20road%20in%20Uttarakhand%20was%20built%20from%20Kotdwar%20to%20Dugadda%20in%20Garhwal.%20So%20far%2C%20mules%20had%20been%20transporting%20goods%20and%20people%20slowly%20and%20painfully%20along%20dangerous%20paths.%20Often%2C%20both%20the%20mules%20and%20rations%20ended%20up%20in%20the%20ravines%20below.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bus%20seemed%20a%20miracle%20to%20the%20locals%20%E2%80%93%2015%2C000%20of%20whom%2C%20according%20to%20old%20papers%2C%20gathered%20to%20see%20the%20first%20bus%20carrying%20a%20precious%20cargo%20of%20jaggery%2C%20grams%20and%20salt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%201909%2C%20the%20motor%20road%20had%20been%20extended%20to%20Lansdowne%20at%20a%20height%20of%201%2C780%20metres%2C%20and%20thence%20to%20Satpuli%20in%201925.%20By%201932%2C%20the%20engineers%20gave%20the%20area%20its%20first%20firm%20wooden%20bridge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInitially%2C%20the%20motor%20road%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egadi%20sadak%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E)%20was%20available%20only%20to%20vehicles%20carrying%20the%20British%20and%20a%20few%20Indian%20VIPs.%20But%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9830s%2C%20one%20Motiram%20of%20Dugadda%20and%20Surajmal%20of%20Kotdwar%20bought%20the%20first%20public%20transport%20buses%20that%20travelled%20via%20Pauri%20to%20Almora.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23135920%2FAlmora-old.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22712%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23135920%2FAlmora-old.jpg%20712w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23135920%2FAlmora-old-300x215.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664633%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22511%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EView%20of%20Almora%2C%20a%20town%20in%20the%20Kumaon%20Himalaya%2C%20in%201895.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FLawrie%20and%20Company%2C%20G.W.%20(Col%20James%20Henry%20Erskine%20Reid).%20Public%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20said%20a%20simple%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPahari%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20woman%20came%20and%20put%20a%20bundle%20of%20grass%20and%20leaves%20before%20the%20stationary%20bus.%20Aha%2C%20like%20her%20cow%2C%20the%20bus%20must%20be%20hungry%20and%20thirsty%20after%20such%20a%20long%20run%2C%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECenturies%20before%20the%20British%20engineers%2C%20the%20locals%20and%20itinerant%20pilgrims%20had%20built%20their%20own%20routes%20that%20led%20to%20the%20holy%20shrines%20and%20glaciers%20in%20the%20area.%20These%20were%20tedious%20treks%20that%20took%20days%20and%20had%20to%20be%20covered%20on%20foot%20with%20a%20little%20bundle%20of%20essentials%20and%20nothing%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20new%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echaudikaran%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(widening)%20of%20old%20roads%20and%20the%20building%20of%20tunnels%20aims%20at%20a%20different%20species%20of%20humans.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20well-heeled%20and%20love%20brief%20vacations%20all%20year%20round.%20Of%20them%2C%20a%20large%20number%20try%20to%20relive%20%E2%80%98the%20Raj%20experience%E2%80%99%2C%20growing%20all%20dewy-eyed%20over%20the%20great%20legacy%20of%20sprawling%20bungalows%2C%20churches%20and%20other%20stately%20buildings%20the%20British%20left%20behind%20for%20us%20in%201947.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20epistemological%20stance%20of%20the%20natives%20yields%20a%20vast%20and%20rare%20treasure%20of%20a%20different%20kind%2C%20laced%20with%20tales%20of%20forced%20unpaid%20labour%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekulli%20begar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E)%20and%20the%20sawing%20down%20of%20precious%20forests.%20The%20tales%20have%20mostly%20oral%20sources%20and%20are%20told%20in%20local%20languages%20that%20few%20Raj%20lovers%20and%20increasingly%20fewer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0local%20people%20speak.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20planners%2C%20to%20be%20sure%2C%20are%20not%20a%20monolithic%20category.%20There%20are%20still%20several%20of%20them%20who%20care%20deeply%20about%20the%20flora%2C%20fauna%20and%20human%20beings%20who%20had%20lived%20in%20harmony%20with%20each%20other%20for%20centuries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20with%20the%20present%20political%20emphasis%20on%20treating%20the%20state%20as%20a%20major%20post%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20empire%2C%20and%20the%20big%20push%20for%20religious%20tourism%20for%20Hindus%2C%20a%20complex%20matrix%20has%20been%20created.%20It%20is%20ruled%20not%20by%20ecological%20concerns%20but%20largely%20by%20vote%20bank%20politics%20and%20the%20money%20ethic%2C%20in%20that%20order.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fbadrinath-redevelopment-must-respect-its-heritage%5C%22%3ERedevelopment%20Projects%20at%20Badrinath%20Must%20Respect%20its%20Unique%20Natural%20and%20Spiritual%20Heritage%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELocal%20papers%20and%20digital%20sites%20regularly%20carry%20articles%20questioning%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reporters-collective.in%2Ftrc%2Fas-cm-lobbied-centre-went-against-rules-courts-to-allow-river-mining-in-uttarakhand%5C%22%3Eexceedingly%20questionable%20steps%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20taken%20in%20the%20name%20of%20development%2C%20and%20the%20banning%20of%20local%20protests%20by%20conservationists.%20The%20overarching%20ambition%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98double-engine%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esarkar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20remains%20unwaveringly%20majoritarian.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECapitalism%20meshes%20well%20with%20a%20segregationist%20mindset.%20The%20hills%20%E2%80%93%20cool%2C%20scenically%20soothing%20and%20picturesque%20spaces%20that%20they%20were%20%E2%80%93%20are%20now%20gradually%20turning%20into%20gated%20communities%20for%20the%20rich%20Indians%20who%20buy%20second%20or%20third%20homes%20here%20for%20vacations%20and%20partying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20the%20British%20before%20them%2C%20the%20hills%20are%20a%20place%20where%20they%20shed%20their%20fatigue%20and%20enjoy%20a%20bit%20of%20fishing%2C%20and%20taste%20a%20bit%20of%20water%20sports%2C%20horse%20riding%20and%20paragliding%20before%20they%20go%20back.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20clever%20builders%E2%80%99%20lobby%20has%20spotted%20a%20golden%20chance%20here%20to%20develop%20clever%20strategies%20to%20help%20outsiders%20buy%20local%20land%20and%20sell%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eit%3Cspan%3E%20to%20their%20clients%20as%20a%20wise%20investment%20for%20their%20future%20generations%20in%20the%20era%20of%20global%20warming.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20still%20a%20direct%20connection%20between%20the%20earlier%20rapid%20urbanisation%20under%20the%20colonial%20government%20through%20%E2%80%9Ccreative%20destruction%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20new%20capital%20accumulation%20(through%20rents%2C%20taxes%2C%20private%20property%20development%2C%20and%20the%20manipulative%20political%2C%20bureaucratic%20and%20real%20estate%20lobbies).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20deeply%20flawed%20development%20paradigm%20of%20various%20governments%20who%20encourage%20the%20extensive%20use%20of%20local%20material%20like%20stone%20and%20timber%20for%20infrastructure%20development%20in%20reserved%20forests%20and%20along%20river%20beds%20leads%20to%20the%20eventual%20destruction%20of%20the%20land%2C%20forests%20and%20rivers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChamoli%20is%20an%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fjoshimath-himalayas-explainer-warnings-reports-construction-ntpc%5C%22%3EJoshimath%20another%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Neglecting%20seemingly%20less%20important%20issues%20like%20providing%20proper%20healthcare%20and%20sanitation%20for%20the%20inhabitants%2C%20along%20well-designed%20%3C%2Fspan%3ESOPs%3Cspan%3E%20and%20safety%20audits%20for%20the%20new%20power%20plants%2C%20have%20major%20consequences%20when%20natural%20disaster%20strikes.%20And%20it%20is%20becoming%20more%20frequent%20with%20ecological%20changes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENature%20is%20its%20own%20protector%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20permitted%20these%20hotels%20on%20top%20of%20the%20river%20in%20the%20first%20place%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocation%3A%20Manali%20Aallu%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FHimachalPradesh%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23HimachalPradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRoXxK5Gmzi%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FRoXxK5Gmzi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Bhavreen%20Kandhari%20(%40BhavreenMK)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBhavreenMK%2Fstatus%2F1678273206166372352%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2010%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20core%20of%20the%20learnings%20from%20the%202013%20Kedar%20Valley%20disaster%20and%20now%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fnorth-india-rains-landslide-floods-toll%5C%22%3EHimachal%20and%20Uttarakhand%20tragedies%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20that%20the%20government%20bulldozing%20its%20way%20into%20the%20hill%20areas%20without%20much%20terrain%20information%20and%20domain%20knowledge%20is%20for%20it%20to%20court%20disaster.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETurning%20away%20from%20available%20data%20and%20expert%20advice%20has%20reconstituted%20and%20reorganised%20both%20the%20topography%20and%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20original%20inhabitants%20in%20ways%20that%20are%20anything%20but%20sustainable%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20The%20new%20planning%20is%20still%20ejecting%20locals%20from%20the%20ownership%20of%20land%20and%20forests%2C%20and%20is%20replacing%20their%20humble%20dwellings%20with%20structures%20that%20are%20ill-suited%20to%20the%20terrain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20ease%20travel%20for%20tourists%2C%20an%20ecologically%20sensitive%20region%20is%20being%20overburdened%20by%20widening%20motorable%20roads%20that%20deliver%20the%20outsiders%20to%20a%20life%20brimming%20with%20sports%20and%20leisure%20institutions%2C%20health%20resorts%20and%20large%20bungalows.%20The%20new%20empire%20in%20the%20hills%20which%20the%20governments%20have%20been%20creating%20is%20a%20sombre%20chronicle%20of%20the%20despoliation%20and%20degradation%20of%20an%20immense%20habitat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20would%20do%20well%20to%20remember%20that%20our%20hills%2C%20forests%20and%20rivers%20are%20neither%20infinite%20nor%20eternal%2C%20and%20colonising%20them%20in%20the%20name%20of%20development%2C%20urbanisation%20or%20tourism%20is%20killing%20them%20with%20fake%20kindness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMrinal%20Pande%20is%20a%20writer%20and%20veteran%20journalist%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690104610000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23141628%2FPauri-Garhwal.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fof-hills-forests-rivers-and-men%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20present%20political%20emphasis%20on%20treating%20Uttarakhand%20as%20a%20major%20post%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20empire%20and%20a%20religious%20tourism%20destination%20presents%20countless%20problems.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fof-hills-forests-rivers-and-men%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Interesting%20Facts%20About%20Oppenheime