that%2012%2C584%20Kuki-Zomi%20people%20from%20Manipur%20have%20been%20housed%20at%20Mizoram%20since%20ethnic%20violence%20began%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMizoram%E2%80%99s%20Meitei%20population%20is%20no%20more%20than%202%2C000.%20Most%20live%20in%20Aizawl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Handed%20over%20by%20Meira%20Paibis%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2F18-year-old-woman-assaulted-gangraped-in-manipur-on-may-15%2Farticle67110455.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported%20that%20an%2018-year-old%20woman%20who%20was%20abducted%2C%20assaulted%20and%20gang-raped%20in%20the%20Imphal%20East%20district%20of%20Manipur%20on%20May%2015%2C%20had%20said%20in%20her%20complaint%20to%20police%20that%20Meira%20Paibi%20women%20had%20%E2%80%9Chanded%20her%20over%20to%20four%20armed%20men.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Meira%20Paibi%20are%20a%20civil%20society%20group%20of%20women%20activists%20and%20belong%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20woman%20approached%20Kangpokpi%20police%20on%20July%2021%2C%20after%20the%20video%20showing%20the%20Thoubal%20district%20crime%20on%20Kuki%20women%20made%20ripples%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20title%3D%5C%22Page%202%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teenaged%20survivor%20had%20been%20admitted%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Nagaland%20with%20severe%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManipur%20in%20the%20UK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConcerns%20over%20Manipur%20were%20also%20brought%20up%20by%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20MP%20Fiona%20Bruce%2C%20who%20serves%20as%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%E2%80%99s%20special%20envoy%20for%20freedom%20of%20religion%20or%20belief%20(FROB).%20During%20a%20session%20in%20the%20main%20chamber%20of%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20on%20Thursday%2C%20MP%20Fiona%20Bruce%20expressed%20alarm%20about%20escalating%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Frishi-sunaks-special-envoy-raises-manipur-violence-in-house-of-commons%2Farticleshow%2F101995573.cms%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20European%20Parliament%20had%20earlier%20adopted%20a%20motion%2C%20denouncing%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20strongest%20terms%20nationalistic%20rhetoric%20deployed%20by%20leading%20members%20of%20the%20BJP%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20oral%20questions%20session%20to%20church%20commissioners%2C%20MP%20Bruce%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20early%20May%20alone%2C%20hundreds%20of%20churches%20have%20been%20destroyed%2C%20many%20burnt%20to%20the%20ground%3B%20over%20100%20people%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20and%20over%2050%2C000%20displaced%3B%20schools%20and%20seminaries%20also%20targeted%20in%20what%20looks%20like%20systematic%20and%20premeditated%20attacks%20with%20religion%20a%20key%20factor.%20Yet%20there%20has%20been%20very%20little%20reporting%20about%20this.%20People%20there%20are%20calling%20out%20for%20help%3B%20what%20can%20the%20Church%20of%20England%20do%20to%20draw%20more%20attention%20to%20their%20cries%3F%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMP%20Bruce%20referred%20to%20a%20report%2C%20produced%20by%20former%20BBC%20reporter%20David%20Campanale%20for%20the%20International%20Religious%20Freedom%20or%20Belief%20Alliance%20(IRFBA)%2C%20which%20she%20chairs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConcerns%20had%20earlier%20been%20raised%20on%20Manipur%20at%20the%20May%2015%20meeting%20of%20the%20Council%20of%20Experts%20to%20IRFBA%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20initiation%20of%20the%20report.%20The%20report%20incorporates%20eyewitness%20testimonies%20from%20victims%20and%20emphasises%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20scale%20of%20the%20destruction%20of%20religious%20places%20of%20worship%20deserves%20far%20wider%20attention%E2%80%A6%20The%20basic%20rights%20to%20freedom%20of%20worship%20and%20assembly%20have%20been%20directly%20impacted%2C%20and%20the%20resources%20required%20to%20rebuild%20churches%20and%20re-establish%20safe%20facilities%20to%20freely%20conduct%20Christian%20services%20will%20be%20significant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInquiring%20about%20the%20Church%20of%20England%E2%80%99s%20recent%20efforts%20to%20protect%20FROB%20in%20other%20countries%2C%20Bruce%20asked%20Selous%2C%20who%20responded%20that%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20has%20recently%20adopted%20a%20resolution%20to%20produce%20an%20annual%20report%20on%20FROB%20sponsored%20by%20the%20UK%20and%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20by%20Campanale%20recommends%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20%E2%80%9Csend%20sufficient%20national%20Indian%20Army%20units%20to%20protect%20tribal%20villages%E2%80%9D%20and%20urges%20a%20comprehensive%20investigation%20into%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20violence%20on%20FROB.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20further%20advocates%20for%20granting%20journalists%20access%20to%20the%20affected%20areas%2C%20convening%20inter-religious%20leaders%20at%20the%20state%20level%20to%20defuse%20tensions%2C%20establishing%20a%20claims%20commission%2C%20and%20restoring%20Internet%20services.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690092481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04223216%2Fimage-968.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-mizoram-meitei-meira-paibi-teenager-fir%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Manipur%20government%20has%20said%20