.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBad%20urban%20planning%20is%20responsible%20for%20our%20conditions%2C%20we%20are%20always%20excluded.%20You%20see%2C%20the%20posh%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20are%20never%20drowned.%20And%20even%20if%20there%E2%80%99s%20water%20in%20those%20places%2C%20they%20do%20not%20face%20the%20torment%20that%20we%20face.%20Rich%20people%20never%20suffer%20from%20these%20curses.%20We%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20are%20perennially%20subjected%20to%20this.%E2%80%99%E2%80%99%20says%20Sangeeta%20(16)%2C%20a%20student%20of%2011th%20standard.%20She%20wanted%20to%20become%20an%20IAS%20officer%20but%20is%20now%20cynical%20about%20it%20since%20the%20flood%20has%20destroyed%20almost%20everything%20that%20their%20family%20had%2C%20leaving%20them%20to%20start%20their%20life%20all%20over%20again%20from%20scratch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNobody%20gave%20us%20any%20warning%20about%20the%20flood.%20There%20was%20no%20official%20announcement%20or%20information.%20All%20my%20books%20were%20drowned.%20Books%20are%20expensive%20and%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20money%20to%20buy%20them%20again.%20I%20am%20going%20to%20school%20from%20this%20relief%20camp%20these%20days%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20books.%20What%20will%20I%20study%3F%20And%20how%20will%20I%20study%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20poor%20people%20but%20we%20are%20also%20residents%20of%20Delhi.%20And%20that%20too%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Our%20fathers%20and%20grandfathers%20have%20lived%20in%20these%20lands.%20We%20gave%20everything%20to%20Delhi.%20We%20built%20the%20city%2C%20we%20grew%20the%20crops.%20We%20spent%20all%20our%20lives%20cleaning%20rich%20people%E2%80%99s%20houses.%20But%20now%20as%20we%20are%20stranded%20in%20these%20camps%2C%20nobody%20has%20any%20problem%20with%20it.%20The%20government%20has%20no%20value%20for%20us.%20Will%20the%20government%20officials%20eat%2