22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fpaul-pogbas-goal-to-end-poverty-as-footballer-launches-new-fund-12925507%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajasthan%20Minimum%20Income%20Law%20Has%20Provided%20a%20Development%20Model%20for%20the%20Nation%3A%20Gehlot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F17105003%2FWIRE-7.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20day%20after%20the%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20passed%20the%20Rajasthan%20Minimum%20Guaranteed%20Income%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20said%20that%20his%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20provide%20social%20security%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20Right.%20Gehlot%20said%20that%20by%20passing%20the%20minimum%20guaranteed%20income%20bill%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20has%20provided%20a%20unique%20development%20model%20to%20the%20country%20and%20hopes%20that%20similar%20laws%20will%20also%20be%20passed%20in%20other%20states%20to%20bring%20every%20citizen%20of%20the%20country%20into%20the%20social%20security%20net.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20a%20law%20and%20an%20administrative%20order.%20The%20minimum%20guaranteed%20income%20bill%20makes%20social%20security%20a%20right.%20The%20minimum%20guaranteed%20income%20law%20is%20historic%20as%20it%20is%20perhaps%20the%20first%20time%20since%20independence%20that%20social%20security%20measures%20like%20pension%20or%20minimum%20days%20of%20work%20have%20been%20brought%20under%20the%20ambit%20of%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gehlot%20said%20on%20Saturday%2C%20July%2022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20law%20guarantees%20125%20days%20of%20work%20for%20all%20families%20of%20the%20state%20and%20a%20minimum%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20as%20a%20pension%20to%20the%20elderly%2C%20women%2C%20widows%2C%20and%20disabled%20people%2C%20with%20the%20provision%20of%20a%2015%25%20increment%20every%20year.%20The%20Bill%20brings%20the%20rural%20employment%20guarantee%20scheme%2C%20the%20urban%20employment%20guarantee%20scheme%2C%20and%20the%20pension%20scheme%20under%20one%20legislation%20that%20will%20be%20implemented%20under%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Minimum%20Income%20Guarantee%20Scheme.%20The%20Bill%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20assembly%20on%20Friday%20through%20a%20voice%20vote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20the%20press%20earlier%20on%20Saturday%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20law%20is%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20similar%20social%20security%20cover%20for%20citizens%20of%20developed%20nations%20like%20the%20US%2C%20England%2C%20Germany%2C%20and%20other%20European%20countries.%20Taking%20a%20dig%20at%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20seen%20such%20a%20law.%20Our%20Prime%20Minister%20claims%20to%20be%20Vishwaguru.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20him%20what%20he%20is%20doing%20about%20problems%20like%20hunger%2C%20malnourishment%2C%20and%20unemployment%20in%20India.%20Why%20is%20not%20making%20social%20security%20a%20right%20for%20140%20crore%20Indians%2C%20a%20figure%20he%20often%20likes%20to%20cite%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGehlot%20said%20that%20the%20law%20was%20merely%20a%20start%2C%20and%20if%20elected%20again%20his%20government%20will%20move%20forward%20in%20the%20direction%20to%20provide%20social%20security%20cover%20to%20all%20in%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20state%20governments%20provide%20very%20poor%20sums%20for%20the%20pension%20scheme.%20The%20union%20government%20gives%20Rs%20200%20as%20a%20pension%20to%20the%20elderly%20and%20Rs%20300%20if%20the%20claimant%20is%20above%2080%20years.%20Tell%20me%20does%20this%20amount%20even%20qualify%20as%20any%20financial%20support%3F%20That%20is%20why%20we%20have%20made%20Rs%201%2C000%20as%20the%20minimum%20support%20to%20the%20pensioners%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20all%20subsequent%20governments%20in%20the%20state%20will%20have%20to%20abide%20by%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20law.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20law%20has%20come%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20next%20assembly%20polls.%20Gehlot%20hoped%20that%20the%20law%20and%20other%20such%20pro-poor%20measures%20will%20help%20it%20win%20the%20elections%20again.%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20talk%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Erevdi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(freebies)%20culture%20are%20distributing%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Erevdis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20states%20that%20they%20govern.%20The%20law%20is%20not%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Erevdi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20a%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gehlot%20said%2C%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRajasthan%20is%20a%20progressive%20state.%20Rajasthan%20was%20also%20the%20first%20state%20to%20implement%20Right%20to%20Information%2C%20Right%20to%20Health%2C%20and%20the%20Minimum%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20before%20it%20became%20national%20laws%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Congress%20chief%20minister%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20new%20law%20will%20be%20financed%20from%20the%20improved%20financial%20health%20of%20the%20state%20under%20his%20leadership.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20not%20introduced%20any%20new%20tax.%20Instead%2C%20our%20revenues%20have%20increased%20by%2017%25.%20Our%20fiscal%20deficit%20has%20also%20come%20down%20from%209.25%25%20from%20the%20time%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20to%20around%203%25%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGehlot%20said%20he%20was%20waiting%20for%20the%20governor%20to%20approve%20the%20law%2C%20and%20hopes%20to%20frame%20the%20rules%20and%20have%20the%20law%20implemented%20by%20August%2015%2C%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20of%20such%20a%20law%20becoming%20a%20burden%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20exchequer%20is%20untrue%2C%20as%20is%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20about%20the%20deteriorating%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20Rajasthan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20NCRB%20figures%2C%20the%20BJP-ruled%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20at%20the%20top%20in%20the%20list%20of%20crimes%20against%20women.%20Gujarat%20is%20ranked%20the%20No.1%20in%20cases%20of%20custodial%20deaths.%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20is%20No.1%20in%20cases%20of%20murders%20and%20kidnapping.%20Rajasthan%20is%20way%20below%20in%20the%20list%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gehlot%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20hike%20in%20some%20of%20the%20crimes%20in%20Rajasthan%20is%20because%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20his%20government%20made%20registering%20FIRs%20compulsory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20increase%20in%20figures%20of%20different%20crimes%20has%20happened%20because%20now%20common%20people%20can%20get%20cases%20registered%20easily%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGehlot%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20should%20answer%20why%20Modi%20could%20not%20deliver%20on%20his%20promise%20of%20generating%202%20crore%20jobs%20every%20year.%20%E2%80%9CToday%20he%20is%20himself%20giving%20appointment%20letters%20to%2080%2C000%20people%20to%20generate%20publicity.%20No%20one%20can%20compete%20with%20Modi%20ji%20in%20marketing.%20He%20came%20to%20Sikar%20and%20said%20that%20he%20is%20spending%20Rs%2020000%20crore%20in%20direct%20benefit%20transfer%20to%209%20crore%20people.%20All%20of%20it%20is%20marketing.%20The%20Rajasthan%20government%20spends%20Rs%2012000%20crore%20in%20subsidising%20electricity%20alone.%20Our%20pension%20scheme%20is%20worth%20around%20Rs%2012-13000%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690034845000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.the