er%20castes%20(Satnami%20caste)%20used%20to%20come%20to%20my%20home%2C%20my%20mother%20used%20to%20not%20say%20anything%20but%20soon%20after%20they%20had%20left%20she%20used%20to%20clean%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20house.%20This%20and%20a%20few%20other%20instances%20deeply%20affected%20me%20and%20I%20realised%20that%20until%20caste%20discrimination%20is%20addressed%20properly%20to%20the%20masses%2C%20society%20would%20not%20progress.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20intent%20on%20these%20issues%20seeing%20the%20light%20of%20day%2C%20Nayak%20began%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291630%2Fsanober-pardiwalla-bollywood-stuntwoman-for-actress-alia-bhatt-deepika-padukone-movies%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equest%20of%20casting%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20song%20recorded%20with%20legend%20Mohammed%20Rafi%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EJhamkat%20nadiya%20bahini%20laage%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20a%20quick%20casting%20of%20theatre%20actors%20who%20were%20willing%2C%20and%20a%20record%2022-day%20packed%20shoot%20schedule%2C%20%3Cem%3EKahi%20Debe%20Sandesh%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20ready%20to%20roll.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Nayak%20says%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20spent%20the%20next%20two%20years%20paying%20off%20my%20debts.%20But%20I%20had%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20making%20the%20first%20Chhattisgarhi%20film.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261909%2Findia-film-project-ritam-bhatanagar-asia-largest-film-festival-content-creators%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20film%3C%2Fa%3E%20continues%20to%20stand%20by%20its%20legacy%20of%20being%20among%20the%20first%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20caste%20discrimination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20cinema%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way