in%20wells%2C%20and%20sometimes%20in%20households.%20This%20puts%20the%20life%20of%20the%20animal%20and%20the%20surrounding%20people%20in%20jeopardy.%20So%20we%20have%20to%20plan%20and%20execute%20everything%20very%20carefully%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20dangerous%20yet%20thrilling%20incident%20recently%2C%20Meghana%20had%20to%20jump%20into%20a%2020-feet-deep%20well%20at%20Niddodi%20in%20Dakshina%20Kannada%20to%20rescue%20a%20leopardess%20stuck%20in%20it%20for%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20well%20was%20quite%20deep%20and%20we%20could%20not%20reach%20the%20leopardess.%20The%20only%20option%20was%20to%20jump%20inside%20to%20sedate%20her%20and%20carry%20her%20up.%20To%20do%20this%2C%20I%20was%20put%20in%20a%20cage%20and%20lowered%20into%20the%20well.%20I%20darted%20at%20the%20leopardess%20at%20close%20range%20and%20waited%20until%20she%20was%20sedated.%20I%20dragged%20her%20into%20my%20cage%20afterwards%20and%20the%20team%20pulled%20us%20both%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeghana%20took%20the%20animal%20under%20her%20care%2C%20examining%20it%20for%20injuries%20and%20providing%20treatment.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20animals%20are%20kept%20under%20observation.%20When%20they%20become%20fit%2C%20we%20take%20them%20to%20their%20real%20home%20%E2%80%94%20the%20wilderness%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDealing%20with%20animal-human%20conflict%20regularly%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F95504%2Fanimal-conservation-human-livelihoods-balance-rajasthan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20animal%20and%20human%20conflict%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eshe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20rapid%20urbanisation%20and%20expansion%20of%20cities%20and%20villages%2C%20we%20have%20encroached%20on%20the%20lands%20that%20were%20supposed%20to%20be%20theirs.%20We%20are%20the%20